Class Rectangle

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.Figure
      • main.Rectangle
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Rectangle>
    public class Rectangle
extends Figure
implements java.lang.Comparable<Rectangle>

    Create Rectangles!

    The Rectangle class implements all the Figure class methods and has some of it's own.

    Note: While creating Rectangle instances do not forget that it takes type doubles as a height and a length.
